      "content": "To project authority and professionalism, focusing on cleanliness, simplicity, and modesty is essential. Suits and dress pants in neutral colors paired with crisp, ironed shirts are generally a safe bet. Charcoal, navy, or black are also popular, as they convey seriousness and authority. Avoid bold patterns, overly casual items, and excessive makeup or jewelry. Remaining well-groomed and well-rested is also crucial to make a great impression.",
