    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I'd also like to get more specific about grooming. Our leadership team is very diverse, so we have people with all sorts of different hair types and styles. For someone who wants to look as \"executive\" and \"polished\" as possible in a boardroom, what kind of hair grooming or styling would you recommend to ensure they don't look too casual or distracting?",
