      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For an executive look, a simple yet neat haircut or style is key. Consider a classic trim, a neat, straight cut, or a well-tapered side part. Hairstyles that are too flashy, wet, or tousled, such as messy waves or celebrity-inspired cuts, can give the wrong impression of a lack of professionalism. A side or bit of a fade also helps keep the look understated yet polished.",
